RBC Bearings (NASDAQ: ROLL) and NN (NASDAQ:NNBR) are both industrial products companies, but which is the better business? We will compare the two companies based on the strength of their earnings, valuation, risk, institutional ownership, dividends, profitabiliy and analyst recommendations. 
Analyst Ratings
